<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify New Contact</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .otp-container {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px dashed #28a745;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .success {
            background: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>âœ… Final Verification Step</h1>
            <p>Verify your new <%= changeType %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= companyName %>,</h2>
            
            <div class="success">
                <strong>âœ… Step 1 Complete:</strong> Your current <%= changeType %> has been verified successfully!
            </div>
            
            <p>Now, please verify your new <%= changeType %> by entering the OTP below:</p>
            
            <div class="otp-container">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: #666;">Your verification code is:</p>
                <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">This code expires in 10 minutes</p>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>ðŸŽ‰ You're almost done!</strong></p>
            <p>Once you verify this OTP, your <%= changeType %> change will be complete and you'll be able to use your new <%= changeType %> for future logins.</p>
            
            <p>For security reasons, this verification code will expire in 10 minutes.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>